title: Want To Buy:  WHY ARE THERE CRAZY INSANE PRICES STILL IN HERE !!!
postcontent:
I'm still seeing 5.56 ammo selling for 1.00 per round.

Why do people think Sig P250's are worth more then 600.00, they run new in 9mm at the gun shops for around 400.00.

Why are there people trying to sell Glocks for around 700.00, when gunshops have them in stock for 500-550.00 price range.

Why are people selling Ruger 22/45LITE's for 500.00 plus, when they sell new at the gun shops for under 400.00.

Some things are coming back to normal, but we still have the people in here that seem to treat this web site as if they are selling guns out of the trunk of their cars in an alley on the east side of Cleveland.

For the ones that seem to do that, you do know that it could be considered a straw purchase, which is a felony.

And I love the ones that buy a gun in on one day really cheap, and the same or next day the same exact gun being sold in here at a 2-300.00 mark up, THAT IS AN FELONY.
